Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}yeah I hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.35,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I care about you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:01.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:04.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:07.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:13.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:17.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:25.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが　どうして　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて　会いたいよなんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:37.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　今日だけは思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:43.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だからあなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:49.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.28,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere yah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:54.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.66,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.96,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:00.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:09.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:19.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我還好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.10,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.06,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我聽到了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.35,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:01.73,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}輕風在長髮間嬉戲著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:04.02,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切都有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:07.32,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}包括那些駐足不前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:13.41,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}到如今我也終於能理解並追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:17.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果不是這雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:25.13,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那麼這麼多看不到的事物 又如何滿溢出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.38,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少 我不會說出想見到你這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:37.06,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我說 只有今天讓我追憶你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:43.10,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以 如果我們能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:49.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一定不再會迷茫 而是選擇當下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:54.82,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.28,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}隨時 隨地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我都會為你歡笑
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.66,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}隨時 隨地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:00.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}每當合上雙眼 總是
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.96,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.50,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算沒有絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.46,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也總能夠傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:09.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算落淚也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.97,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因為黎明一定會來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:19.22,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我會為你的歸來輕聲歌唱著我們搖籃曲
